description.en:
W-WIFI (WIFI) is a blockchain-based project that aims to provide its users with a fast and reliable Wi-Fi connection with the highest blockchain security level. Through W-WIFI, users can experience various internet bandwidth in different areas covered by W-WIFI at affordable price packages.

On the other hand, merchants and business owners can benefit from the promotions and business packages that W-WIFI offers. With the W-WIFI app, enterprises and businesses can easily gain access to their target audience, enabling their product to be more visible and stand out among others globally.
